43推 1:1 In the beginning was the Word, and the Word was with God, and the Word was God.
43推 1:2 He was in the beginning with God.
43推 1:3 All things came into being by Him, and apart from Him nothing came into being that has come into being.
43推 1:4 In Him was life, and the life was the light of men.
