43推 1:48 Nathanael *said to Him, "How do You know me?" Jesus answered and said to him, "Before Philip called you, when you were under the fig tree, I saw you."
43推 1:49 Nathanael answered Him, "Rabbi, You are the Son of God; You are the King of Israel."
43推 1:50 Jesus answered and said to him, "Because I said to you that I saw you under the fig tree, do you believe? You shall see greater things than these."
43推 1:51 And He *said to him, "Truly, truly, I say to you, you shall see the heavens opened, and the angels of God ascending and descending on the Son of Man."
43推 2:1 And on the third day there was a wedding in Cana of Galilee, and the mother of Jesus was there;
